<a class='reflink' href='../2.sg/2.1.uacl.html#footnote21differentdiam'>Footnote</a>

<div class='toload footnote'>
	<p>
	The same theory can be developed, almost word-by-word, for any other choice of uniform bound for the diameters. Alternatively, every bounded metric space can be normalized to diameter $1$.
	</p>
</div>